ffles topped with creamy, dreamy scoops of ice cream. A perfect balance of warm and cold, crunchy and smooth—an irresistible dessert delight!', '135.00', 'croffles', 'false', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/menu-images/1756714638131-fab039za8n.jpg', '2025-08-30 06:45:52.48103+00', '2026-01-06 02:12:21.996671+00', 'true'), ('0f79e4dc-c8e2-47e3-bbee-7910636a4e3f', 'PEACH ICED TEA', 'This iced tea is smooth, fragrant, and naturally bright—served chilled to bring a crisp, fruity finish that cools you down with every sip. Light, uplifting, and deliciously peachy, it’s the perfect drink for warm days or anytime you want a burst of fresh flavor.', '60.00', 'non-coffee', 'false', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/menu-images/1763096538808-uu7y56br4ts.jpeg', '2025-11-14 05:02:28.074345+00', '2025-12-31 05:03:21.904043+00', 'true'), ('104e3f30-32e0-4ed7-bbae-2e890d7fc237', 'SAMYANG BULDAK QUATTRO', 'A bold fusion of four intense flavors—spicy, cheesy, creamy, and smoky—in one unforgettable fiery noodle experience.', '125.00', 'diy-korean-ramen', 'false', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/menu-images/1756733172474-1zlmp42h8sj.webp', '2025-09-01 13:26:19.117039+00', '2025-09-01 13:26:19.117039+00', 'true'), ('105142c7-dbd9-4fa2-8b1f-f181f74afe1d', 'CUCUMBER LEMONADE GLASS', 'A crisp, cooling blend of fresh cucumber and zesty lemonade. Light, revitalizing, and perfect for a refreshing twist on a classic favorite!', '40.00', 'non-coffee', 'false', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/menu-images/1756727344558-viru5wvzrsl.jpg', '2025-09-01 11:49:36.058977+00', '2026-01-08 10:02:16.513691+00', 'false'), ('176c2d25-cbaa-4974-8d08-01a2d39980a9', 'ICED CAFE MOCHA', 'A classic blend of espresso, steamed milk, and chocolate for a sweet and bold coffee experience', '160.00', 'iced-coffee', 'false', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/p